// 库表总览（与 init.sql 中全部 CREATE TABLE 一致）
// 黑灰白风格；cluster margin 控制圆角表格外缘与虚线框间距。
// ranksep（英寸）是层间「最小」间距；真实缝 = max(ranksep, 排版约束)。ranksep 过小且节点设了 height 时，易与文字高度打架，出现压扁或缝忽大忽小。
// 勿加 equally，否则短列缝易被均匀拉大。
// nodesep：同一层上各列圆角框之间的水平间距（列与列之间）。
// 勿对「不同 cluster」内首节点使用全局 rank=same，否则首格易被画在虚线框外。
// 导出：dot -Tpng -Gdpi=200 cdiom_db_tables_overview.dot -o cdiom_db_tables_overview.png

digraph CDIOM_DB_Tables_Overview {
  graph [
    rankdir=TB
    bgcolor=white
    fontname="Microsoft YaHei"
    fontsize=9
    fontcolor="#1a1a1a"
    label="库表总览"
    labelloc=t
    nodesep=0.6
    ranksep=0.032
    margin=0.18
    splines=none
  ];
  node [
    shape=box
    style="rounded,filled"
    fillcolor="#f0f0f0"
    color="#1a1a1a"
    penwidth=0.9
    fontname="Consolas"
    fontsize=5
    fontcolor="#000000"
    margin="0.06,0.018"
  ];
  edge [style=invis, weight=100];

  subgraph cluster_1 {
    margin=8;
    label="系统核心";
    labelloc=t;
    fontsize=7;
    fontname="Microsoft YaHei";
    fontcolor="#000000";
    style="rounded,dashed";
    color="#2a2a2a";
    fillcolor="#d0d0d0";

    sys_role;
    sys_user;
    sys_config;
    sys_notice;
    operation_log;
    login_log;
  }

  subgraph cluster_2 {
    margin=8;
    label="权限控制";
    labelloc=t;
    fontsize=7;
    fontname="Microsoft YaHei";
    fontcolor="#000000";
    style="rounded,dashed";
    color="#2a2a2a";
    fillcolor="#d0d0d0";

    sys_user_role;
    sys_permission;
    sys_role_permission;
    sys_user_permission;
  }

  subgraph cluster_3 {
    margin=8;
    label="供货数据";
    labelloc=t;
    fontsize=7;
    fontname="Microsoft YaHei";
    fontcolor="#000000";
    style="rounded,dashed";
    color="#2a2a2a";
    fillcolor="#d0d0d0";

    supplier;
    drug_info;
    supplier_drug_agreement;
    supplier_drug;
    supplier_drug_price_history;
  }

  subgraph cluster_4 {
    margin=8;
    label="仓储业务";
    labelloc=t;
    fontsize=7;
    fontname="Microsoft YaHei";
    fontcolor="#000000";
    style="rounded,dashed";
    color="#2a2a2a";
    fillcolor="#d0d0d0";

    inventory;
    purchase_order;
    purchase_order_item;
    inbound_receipt_batch;
    inbound_record;
    outbound_apply;
    outbound_apply_item;
    inventory_adjustment;
    favorite_drug;
  }

  subgraph cluster_5 {
    margin=8;
    label="准入审批";
    labelloc=t;
    fontsize=7;
    fontname="Microsoft YaHei";
    fontcolor="#000000";
    style="rounded,dashed";
    color="#2a2a2a";
    fillcolor="#d0d0d0";

    supplier_approval_application;
    supplier_approval_item;
    supplier_blacklist;
    price_warning_config;
    supplier_approval_log;
  }

  /* 各分区内部：自上而下竖链 */
  sys_role -> sys_user -> sys_config -> sys_notice -> operation_log -> login_log;
  sys_user_role -> sys_permission -> sys_role_permission -> sys_user_permission;
  supplier -> drug_info -> supplier_drug_agreement -> supplier_drug -> supplier_drug_price_history;
  inventory -> purchase_order -> purchase_order_item -> inbound_receipt_batch -> inbound_record
    -> outbound_apply -> outbound_apply_item -> inventory_adjustment -> favorite_drug;
  supplier_approval_application -> supplier_approval_item -> supplier_blacklist -> price_warning_config
    -> supplier_approval_log;

  supplier_approval_application [margin="0.15,0.018"];
}
